column5: Wishing everyone a great spring and steelhead season!!!  Got this brute earlier this week.
Nice, me and the wife are headed out in the morning.
Nice fish,were not far behind you!!!!
That's a beast! I'm gonna give'r a go tomorrow morning. With my luck at steelheading, I'll come home with a cold.
Wow! What a pig! Nice job!!
That's a nice start to the season! WTG.
Sweet way to usher in the spring. Nice fish.
Nice fish! Can't wait for this ice to melt!
